OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney says he's
OL,7,F"absolutely horrified" by reports
OL,8,Falleging a hidden camera had been
OL,9,Fplaced in the toilets at Holyrood.
OL,11,FHis comments follow allegations that
OL,12,FSouth Scotland Colin Smyth MSP had
OL,13,Fplaced a hidden camera in the Scottish
OL,14,FParliament building, which he denies.
OL,16,FThe SNP leader said he was "extremely
OL,17,Fconcerned" about the implications for
OL,18,FMSPs, staff and journalists who use
OL,19,Fthe Holyrood building.
