OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,FMr Smith was charged with a separate
OL,7,Foffence of possessing indecent images,
OL,8,Fprompting his suspension from Scottish
OL,9,FLabour on 5 August 2025. His access to
OL,10,FHolyrood was deactivated two days
OL,11,Flater.
OL,13,FWith MSPs due to return following
OL,14,Fsummer recess tomorrow, the First
OL,15,FMinister said: "I'm absolutely
OL,16,Fhorrified by what has been the subject
OL,17,Fof revelations over the course of the
OL,18,Flast few weeks.
