OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,F"I'm extremely concerned about what
OL,7,Fthe implications are for members of
OL,8,Fparliament, members of staff,
OL,9,Fjournalists, for everyone who uses the
OL,10,Fparliamentary building."
OL,12,FThe First Minister is urging
OL,13,Fparliamentary authorities to provide
OL,14,F"clear and definitive reassurance to
OL,15,Feverybody involved."
OL,17,FPolice Scotland confirmed a search of
OL,18,Fthe toilets and changing rooms had
OL,19,Fbeen carried out across the Parliament
OL,20,Fbuilding, with "no covert recording
OL,21,Fdevices" found on 29 August 2025.
