OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,FPeople using the building have been
OL,7,Ftold there will be "enhanced
OL,8,Fadditional checks" going forward.
OL,10,FIn a statement at the time, Colin
OL,11,FSmyth MSP said: "This allegation has
OL,12,Fcome as an utter shock and one I
OL,13,Fstrongly refute.
OL,15,F"For legal reasons, I can't respond to
OL,16,Fspecific matters or speculation, and I
OL,17,Fappreciate there is a process to go
OL,18,Fthrough which I am, of course, fully
OL,19,Fcooperating with. But I sincerely hope
OL,20,Fit can be concluded quickly and fairly.
