OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,F"The speculation, and the recent
OL,7,Fdecision by the police to publicly
OL,8,Frelease details of their ongoing
OL,9,Finquiries along with my home address,
OL,10,Fhas been devastating and has taken a
OL,11,Fserious toll on my health.
OL,13,F"After my address was published with
OL,14,Fno warning to my family, I felt I had
OL,15,Fno choice but to move away to protect
OL,16,Fthem.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
