OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,F"That has also meant losing the local
OL,7,FNHS critical support I had been
OL,8,Freceiving for the past few weeks,
OL,9,Fmaking an already difficult time even
OL,10,Fmore distressing.
OL,12,F"I would therefore ask that the
OL,13,Fprivacy of myself, but above all, my
OL,14,Ffamily and friends, is respected while
OL,15,Fthis matter is resolved. Having this
OL,16,Fhanging over them is especially
OL,17,Foverwhelming".
