OL,3,CFirst Minister John Swinney reacts to
OL,4,Creports of secret camera in Holyrood
OL,6,FSpeaking at Glasgow Caledonian
OL,7,FUniversity on Monday, Scottish Labour
OL,8,Fleader Anas Sarwar said: "It's deeply
OL,9,Fdistressing and shocking for all of us
OL,10,Fand for people across the
OL,11,Fparliamentary estate, no doubt.
OL,13,F"As soon as we became aware of the
OL,14,Fseriousness of the allegations, Colin
OL,15,FSmyth was suspended. He now sits as an
OL,16,Findependent MSP.
